Original: Did you folks hear? They've finally
made it down to [Color:5]B3F[Color:0]... unexplored
territory in the Lush Woodlands.
[Page]
This upstart guild called [Guild]
is supposed to have done it.
[Page]
We can't let them show us up.
Look out, red bears! Me and my clan
are coming to get you!

Original: Have you met the [Color:5]Vessels[Color:0]? I came
across them when I was exploring
the Ravine at night.
[Page]
Those poisonous claws and long tails
of theirs... They were howling so
madly, I couldn't get a word in.
[Page]
I got scared and hit one without
thinking. I guess I wasn't keeping
enough of an open mind...

Original: Oh, hello. Is everything going okay
with your trips to the Echoing

lies ahead of the [Color:5]dog statue[Color:0] in that

couldn't budge it. How do you get that
thing to move...?
